\c 7
\s Ubuqili bowesifazana omubi
\p
\v 1 Ndodana yami, gcina amazwi ami\x + 2.1.\x*, uzibekele imilayo yami\x + 2.1.\x*.
\v 2 Gcina imilayo yami\x + 4.4.\x*, uphile\x + 4.4.\x*, lomthetho wami njengenhlamvu yamehlo akho\x + Dute. 32.10.\x*.
\v 3 Ukubophele eminweni yakho\x + 3.3.\x*, kubhale esibhebheni senhliziyo yakho\x + 3.3.\x*.
\v 4 Uthi kunhlakanipho: Ungudadewethu; ubize ukuqedisisa \add ngokuthi\add* yisihlobo sakho\x + Ruthe 2.1. Ruthe 3.2.\x*;
\v 5 ukuze kukugcine kumfazi wemzini\x + 2.16.\x*, kowesifazana wemzini oyengayo ngamazwi akhe\x + 2.16.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Ngoba ewindini lendlu yami\x + Hlu. 5.28.\x*, ngeminxibo yewindi ngalunguza phandle\x + Hlu. 5.28.\x*,
\v 7 ngasengibona phakathi kwabangelalwazi\x + 1.4.\x*, ngananzelela phakathi kwabatsha ijaha eliswele ingqondo\x + 6.32.\x*,
\v 8 lisedlula esitaladeni\x + Tshu. 12.4,5.\x* eceleni kwengonsi yakhe\x + 7.12.\x*, linyathela endleleni yendlu yakhe,
\v 9 kusihlwa, ngentambama yosuku\x + Jobe 24.15.\x*, ebusuku obumnyama, lomnyama\x + 20.20.\x*.
\v 10 Khangela-ke, owesifazana walihlangabeza, \add le\add*sembatho sewule, elobuqili ngenhliziyo\x + Hlab. 73.6. Gen. 38.14.\x*.
\v 11 Lo wayelomsindo\x + 9.13.\x*, eyisiqholo\x + Hlab. 68.6.\x*; inyawo zakhe kazihlali endlini yakhe\x + 5.6. 1 Tim. 5.13. Tit. 2.5.\x*.
\v 12 Khathesi uphandle, abesesiba ezitaladeni, ecathama kuyo\x + 23.28.\x* yonke ingonsi\x + 7.12.\x*.
\v 13 Ngokunjalo walibamba, walanga, waqinisa ubuso bakhe, wathi kulo:
\v 14 Imihlatshelo yeminikelo yokuthula ikimi\x + Levi 7.11.\x*; lamuhla \add se\add*ngibhadele izifungo zami\x + Hlab. 50.14.\x*.
\v 15 Ngakho-ke ngiphumile ukukuhlangabeza, ngidingisise ubuso bakho; ngikutholile\x + 1.28.\x*.
\v 16 Ngendlele umbheda wami ngezendlalo\x + 31.22.\x*, ngamalembu acolekileyo kakhulu alemibalabala avela eGibhithe\x + 1 Kho. 10.28. Isa. 19.9.\x*.
\v 17 Ngifafazile umbheda wami\x + Hlab. 68.9.\x* \w ngemure\w**\x + Joha. 19.39.\x*, izinhlaba\x + Joha. 19.39.\x*, \w lekinamoni\w**\x + Eks. 30.23.\x*.
\v 18 Woza, sizidakise ngothando kuze kuse, sizithokozise ngothando olukhulu.
\v 19 Ngoba indoda kayikho endlini yayo, ihambile uhambo khatshana\x + Mat. 20.11.\x*.
\v 20 Ithethe isaka lemali esandleni sayo; ngosuku lwenyanga egcweleyo izakuza endlini yayo\x + Gen. 42.35.\x*.
\v 21 Walihuga ngobunengi bemfundiso yakhe\x + Jobe 11.4.\x*, walivumisa ngenkulumo zakhe ezincengayo\x + 6.24. 5.3.\x*.
\v 22 Lahle lamlandela njengenkabi isiya ekuhlatshweni, lanjengesiphukuphuku sisiya ekujezisweni esongweni lenqagala;
\v 23 uze umtshoko uhlabe isibindi salo, njengenyoni iphangisela esifwini, ingazi ukuthi simelene lempilo yayo\x + Tshu. 9.12.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Khathesi-ke, bantwana, ngizweni\x + 5.7.\x*\x + 4.1.\x*, lilalele amazwi omlomo wami\x + 4.1.\x*.
\v 25 Inhliziyo yakho kayingaphambukeli endleleni zakhe; ungaduhi emikhondweni yakhe\x + 4.15.\x*.
\v 26 Ngoba ubawisele phansi abanengi abalimeleyo, labo bonke ababuleweyo bakhe banengi\x + Hlu. 16.1-5. Neh. 13.26.\x*.
\v 27 Indlu yakhe izindlela zesihogo\x + 2.18. 5.5. 9.18.\x*, ezehlela emakamelweni okufa\x + Isa. 14.18.\x*.